00:00.010 --> 00:01.200
<i>Previously on Boston Legal…</i>

00:01.240 --> 00:02.410
I'm no psychologist,

00:02.450 --> 00:05.600
but I believe the best way to
relieve anxiety is to talk about it.

00:05.640 --> 00:06.370
Humperdinck.

00:06.410 --> 00:07.880
Clearly I make you uncomfortable.

00:07.920 --> 00:08.570
What is it?

00:08.610 --> 00:11.410
Mr Washington, you were
convicted of rape in 1985?

00:11.450 --> 00:12.910
Date rape, and I was innocent.

00:12.950 --> 00:14.140
You were convicted, yes or no?

00:14.180 --> 00:15.360
She was my girlfriend.

00:15.400 --> 00:16.490
She was 16.

00:16.500 --> 00:18.290
I was 17. And she was white.

00:18.330 --> 00:20.910
She claimed that I
raped her, but I did not.

00:20.950 --> 00:23.270
So you were convicted of rape.

00:23.280 --> 00:25.100
In review, didn't do this one.

00:25.140 --> 00:26.980
You were framed. You
didn't commit the rape.

00:27.020 --> 00:27.920
The victim made it up.

00:27.960 --> 00:30.600
I am innocent of this crime.

