00:47.200 --> 00:49.280
I'm looking for Alan Shore.

00:50.060 --> 00:50.810
It's important.

00:50.850 --> 00:53.090
–Is he expecting you?
–No.

00:53.600 --> 00:56.108
May I tell him what this is regarding?

00:56.110 --> 00:57.660
No.

00:58.370 --> 01:00.940
Okay. Just a minute. I'll…

01:08.350 --> 01:08.940
Okay.

01:08.950 --> 01:10.870
Thank you for agreeing to see me.

01:10.910 --> 01:15.180
Well, my assistant said
it, uh, was some sort of emergency.

01:15.190 --> 01:18.040
Yes, my daughter was murdered.

01:20.750 --> 01:22.580
I'm very sorry.

01:22.960 --> 01:27.350
The man who murdered her was found not
guilty by reason of temporary insanity.

01:27.390 --> 01:30.580
He's a man of means
with skilled attorneys.

01:32.890 --> 01:35.940
And how exactly can I help you?

01:35.950 --> 01:40.720
I would like to kill this man and be found
not guilty by reason of temporary insanity.

01:40.760 --> 01:46.898
I would like you to advise me as to what legal
steps I must take in order to accomplish this.

01:48.130 --> 01:50.860
Uh, Ms Kelly, I don't know
what you've heard about me,

01:50.900 --> 01:55.990
but… I certainly would not
and could not advise a person…

01:56.000 --> 01:59.500
on how to… get away with murder.

01:59.510 --> 02:01.250
Why not?

02:01.850 --> 02:04.400
Well, because that would me
a conspirator, for starters,

02:04.440 --> 02:09.550
and personally, I'm not a
great believer in murdering.

02:11.210 --> 02:12.860
Let me start over.

02:12.870 --> 02:14.370
I have decided to write a novel.

02:14.410 --> 02:18.770
It's about a woman who kills a man and
is acquitted on grounds of insanity.

02:18.810 --> 02:20.810
I would like to hire
you as a consultant.

02:20.850 --> 02:26.690
What legal steps must my protagonist
take in order to accomplish this?

02:27.260 --> 02:29.660
You cannot be serious.

02:31.740 --> 02:34.630
On a positive note, I can tell
you— for what it's worth—

02:34.670 --> 02:36.540
you seem totally insane.

02:36.550 --> 02:37.940
Thank you.

02:37.950 --> 02:40.510
How best do I legally establish that?

02:40.520 --> 02:42.930
I need to know exactly.

02:43.950 --> 02:47.800
MsKelly, my advice to
you… would be to forget it.

02:47.810 --> 02:50.080
By virtue of the fact
that you've come here,

02:50.120 --> 02:55.980
you've demonstrated that you understand
the nature and quality of the act.

02:56.470 --> 03:01.690
As for legal insanity, you don't qualify.

03:06.400 --> 03:08.780
I'm disappointed.

