–Yeah

40:46.570 --> 40:47.920
Terrible.

40:50.130 --> 40:54.222
I used to think hope was something
that belonged to everybody.

40:54.580 --> 41:00.080
Put limits on guns
and butter but hope…

41:01.330 --> 41:03.540
Springs a kernel.

41:06.110 --> 41:07.750
Old farmer's saying.

41:07.760 --> 41:09.280
Growing corn?

41:09.290 --> 41:11.400
Hope springs a kernel.

41:11.410 --> 41:13.310
Haven't you heard that?

41:14.140 --> 41:16.560
Springs eternal.

41:18.040 --> 41:21.890
Hope… springs eternal.

41:26.640 --> 41:28.470
It didn't for Joseph Washington.

41:28.510 --> 41:30.890
Or if it did, it didn't matter.

41:32.140 --> 41:34.690
Two things this world
has too much of:

41:34.700 --> 41:36.820
suffering and…

41:38.560 --> 41:40.090
corn.

41:40.790 --> 41:43.610
I think it is hope springs a kernel.

